<!-- ====== ABOUT ====== -->
<section class="about" id="about">
  <img src="{{ 'molecule.svg' | asset_url }}" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="about__molecule">
  <div class="about__container">
    <div class="about__content fade-in">
      <p class="about__eyebrow">About Kyn</p>
      <h2 class="about__heading">Built for skin like yours.</h2>
      <div class="about__body">
        <p>Kyn Skyn was created for people with fungus-prone skin. Conditions like seborrheic dermatitis, fungal acne, and Malassezia-related irritation show up differently on darker skin, yet are rarely represented in the skincare space. Most products on the market contain lipids that feed Malassezia, making things worse. Ours don't.</p>
        <p>Our name is inspired by kin: a nod to connection, community, and care. Every formula and visual choice honors that ethos.</p>
        <p>Our first product, Steady Serum, is a residue-light formula that helps reduce the look of flakes and oil while respecting your skin and scalp ecosystem. Formulated with lightweight MCT oil, it delivers long-lasting hydration without feeding Malassezia.</p>
      </div>
      <svg class="about__mark" viewBox="0 0 111 106" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M109.661 41.6249C98.2664 41.6249 87.4172 37.3581 79.14 29.6186C70.9252 21.957 65.8902 11.5703 64.9706 0.358164V0H45.1895V0.358164C44.2854 11.5703 39.2504 21.9726 30.9888 29.6497C22.6649 37.3892 11.8313 41.656 0.498814 41.656H0.0935277L0 60.6387H0.405287C25.2525 60.6387 45.4544 80.7737 45.4544 105.534V105.923H64.5029V105.534C64.5029 80.7893 84.7205 60.6387 109.568 60.6387H110.16V41.656H109.646L109.661 41.6249Z" fill="currentColor"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="about__images fade-in">
      <div class="about__image-wrap img-tall">
        <img src="{{ 'gabby-closeup.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Gabby" style="object-position: center 15%;">
        <div class="about__image-overlay">
          <span class="about__image-overlay-title">The Kyn.</span>
          <span class="about__image-overlay-sub">Made by us, for us.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about__image-wrap">
        <img src="{{ 'kiiren-closeup.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Kiiren" style="object-position: center 20%;">
        <div class="about__image-overlay">
          <span class="about__image-overlay-title">Malassezia.</span>
          <span class="about__image-overlay-sub">Doesn't run the show.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about__image-wrap">
        <img src="{{ 'kwamena-smile.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Kwamena" style="object-position: center 15%;">
        <div class="about__image-overlay">
          <span class="about__image-overlay-title">The Skyn.</span>
          <span class="about__image-overlay-sub">Built by people who get it,<br>because they have it.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
