      <h2 class="handbook-teaser__heading">The Fungal Skin Handbook.</h2>
      <p class="handbook-teaser__desc">A plain-English guide to managing Malassezia skin conditions. Everything we wish someone had explained about seb derm, dandruff, fungal acne, tinea versicolor, and related conditions.</p>

      <div class="handbook-teaser__topics">
        <span class="handbook-teaser__tag">Seb Derm</span>
        <span class="handbook-teaser__tag">Fungal Acne</span>
        <span class="handbook-teaser__tag">Tinea Versicolor</span>
        <span class="handbook-teaser__tag">Safe Ingredients</span>
        <span class="handbook-teaser__tag">Skin of Color</span>
        <span class="handbook-teaser__tag">Treatment Guides</span>
